object.moment_title: Enick Dan completed day 352 of the Plan, Top Verses to Memorize

object.content:
What have I learnt today?

It pays to live a godly life and be content. It prevents unnecessary stress and worry. 

I must learn to speak out for people because God sees the heart.

I must live righteously. A spiritual man is a man of knowledge. I must seek knowledge and wisdom above all else

It is hard to read books but I must be persistent.

object.content: Let God bless me. I should refrain from living an unhealthy lifestyle of overworking myself without concentration
Angels carry out the plans and commands of God. They do God's will and are able to praise God
Not the spiritually poor but the materially poor. He listened to their prayer because they lack a sustainable source of income

The reward of loving the Lord
- Rescue
- Protection
- Answered prayers
- God's presence in trouble
- Honour
- Long life
- Salvation
